"userName":"罪のM豆","userSign":"(《2001》天下第一！)","message":"我认为是【代入感】和【亲近感】<br>先说后者，也就是在尽量接近现实的感情发展下进行创作，不是说毫无铺垫就Kiss，发糖什么的——这显得很不现实，少女漫找的是恋爱感不是419<br>再说前者，既然是少女漫，我觉得要能够让女性观众再看的时候有代入感，做简单的做法就是把女主角弄得尽量平凡一些<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>在这个基准上，创造讨喜的男角色吧<br>胡说八道一点吧<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/86/318696.jpg","floor":"#16-1","id":"1239409","time":"2017-5-22 00:04","userId":"318696","userName":"八千万","userSign":"","message":"总裁写出来太尬了，满满的羞耻感"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/60/106075.jpg","floor":"#17","id":"1235421","time":"2017-5-10 21:43","userId":"needxuyao","userName":"XN","userSign":"","message":"<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/book/tag/少女漫画/?sort=rank\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://bgm.tv/book/tag/少女漫画/?sort=rank</a><br>猜猜第一是哪部漫画，哈哈","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/35/273543.jpg","floor":"#17-1","id":"1235427","time":"2017-5-10 22:11","userId":"hydrilla","userName":"黑藻","userSign":"","message":"这tag是有意的吧233"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/35/333500.jpg","floor":"#17-2","id":"1235561","time":"2017-5-11 20:35","userId":"333500","userName":"山鲁佐德","userSign":"","message":"没毛病<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#17-3","id":"1239446","time":"2017-5-22 09:10","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"是这样的啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/30/133075.jpg","floor":"#18","id":"1235426","time":"2017-5-10 22:10","userId":"liaune","userName":"君寻","userSign":"(学会欣赏不完美)","message":"最重要的是要有真情<br>既然是少女漫，男主肯定不能虚情假意、见异思迁，然后对女主一见钟情，不能开后宫，女主倒是可以开个后宫<br>日常搞笑可以有，但不要强行搞笑，如果没什么必要，宁可不要搞笑，多注重一下感情发展，心理描写，我觉得还好一些","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/86/318696.jpg","floor":"#18-